{"tid":2000120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家要培養「減低同路人嘅成本」嘅mindset","createTime":"2020-05-03T15:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T17:36:03.000Z","uid":71237,"like":138,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5eeed5c1b0a2ce5031a0940caed42d66a0fea550","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"無論喺連登、網絡世界定係現實生活，大家都可以盡量諗下點樣減低同路人嘅成本。<br />\n<br />\n以黃色經濟圈為例，有人製作咗黃店地圖、黃店apps，就可以大幅減低尋找黃店嘅成本。大家省返啲時間，就可以用嚟做更多有意義嘅嘢。<br />\n就算每人只係節省到幾分鐘，長遠累積落嚟嘅效果都會好大。<br />\n<br />\n又例如唔同戰線(twitter/TVB/維基百科)都有寫教學文章，訓練新手加入戰線，寫多啲教學文章都係減低自己人成整<br />\n本嘅方法。"},{"pid":"7335d3e790f56af6cc48f374e3b4612bd80f654a","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:40:41.000Z","msg":"平時同自己人whatsapp傾計，可以多啲打字或者用語音轉文字，等對方唔洗聽成分鐘錄音。<br />\n<br />\n連登開post唔好做標題黨，喺標題大約總結下個post嘅中心思想，都可以節省到少少自己人嘅時間。"},{"pid":"36f732c520f7b732326f521447f00a01377a517a","tid":2000120,"uid":92017,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"幫你推下, 由高登睇你出repeat警世post睇到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c8081d9acbbffad1939cb1dcd1a5ea41b47a16","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"就算抗爭以外都好多嘢可以節省其他人嘅時間。<br />\n例如你係一個鍾意睇netflix嘅人，你都可以整張list出嚟講下有咩好睇、有咩唔好睇，都可以節省到大家嘅時間。"},{"pid":"abc37f54c13d7ad84e7c4ed7a48d6080bfdd5bbf","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36f732c520f7b732326f521447f00a01377a517a","tid":2000120,"uid":92017,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:45:46.000Z","msg":"幫你推下, 由高登睇你出repeat警世post睇到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"多謝 😄😄"},{"pid":"243f38c05237c7fcba5e4c86052b1fbb99f1649f","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:50:51.000Z","msg":"如果你係大學生，可以向師弟分享下讀書、搵intern心得<br />\n互相share下資源"},{"pid":"1ef6d15d3c89c96eab64341378e823d33e41a252","tid":2000120,"uid":42691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"同意 <br />\n應該珍惜自己既時間<br />\n浪費對家時間"},{"pid":"abe336c74cc15f3fa019036ca88e42667f901e00","tid":2000120,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a003acdc4f02fdc68281dbaeb1ebf7141b7763d6","tid":2000120,"uid":79085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"88ffc67708392daafd799d85c2b9dc9f1b94f3f4","tid":2000120,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903e6f0501c8f7c80e5ef98fda6e0315e8f3d82b","tid":2000120,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"支持一下"},{"pid":"883907a86c3870773159d03d905672148d1455c1","tid":2000120,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />strong po"},{"pid":"0f36fe490c4c77988bbb1707373d7bec2c47f47e","tid":2000120,"uid":54564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f4944014dd72042086e5845616c8d502ef44f","tid":2000120,"uid":92007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:29:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6372e433660ed4ee496a1eb064cbe836f088a8d","tid":2000120,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e4340701266f04bdc694941e4e05692c13b4e2f","tid":2000120,"uid":10249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"所以我成日幫啲女做足前戲 佢投入時我都爽啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e95c0f39c9e8c4cd147934c6c010427068dabfaf","tid":2000120,"uid":43763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:36:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n舊登有睇你講econ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f743a4ac8d89b1e076d80722ab6adfd2d85679","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1ef6d15d3c89c96eab64341378e823d33e41a252","tid":2000120,"uid":42691,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T15:53:05.000Z","msg":"同意 <br />\n應該珍惜自己既時間<br />\n浪費對家時間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T16:38:49.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n自己付出嘅成本要低過對家付出嘅成本<br />\n<br />\n好似之前嘅$1交稅大法咁<br />\n如果你人手去做，就係浪費緊自己時間<br />\n但如果用bot去做，就係十分成功"},{"pid":"bd5c9a98a94945a3b3354ecf532cfdac65c1e6aa","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:34:32.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀<br />\n<br />\n黃圈要長遠發展，好多嘢要一層一層疊上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2000249\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2000249</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"275bb4554bf803419a28d943fd2dfd7344b050c5","tid":2000120,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a46464d8b342c92f50e10d591e7200dec7ee7f","tid":2000120,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe991f38db79a9fc46b9778108669f1b1a2b0a9f","tid":2000120,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T18:32:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748823f66092e502e5bb5085cd71200adddbbd23","tid":2000120,"uid":84781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T19:54:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f896b3131d9fe982472343360f9ccd4c96e976e","tid":2000120,"uid":306340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T20:09:34.000Z","msg":"時間係成本嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a82c73923cd407cf61d049084118b96f1005e6","tid":2000120,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T00:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e5e373fd93673f57dae972e622f267eda452da23","tid":2000120,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T02:27:36.000Z","msg":"大家都可以睇下以下文章：<br />\n<br />\n由效益角度分析抗爭：<br />\n鍵盤戰士唔應該停留喺低成本抗爭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1775722/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n「無成本，點解唔做？」好多人都誤解咗成本的概念。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1565102/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1565102/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要培養「減低同路人嘅成本」嘅mindset<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000120/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000120/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n評論唔同嘅抗爭方法：<br />\n1. 論「聯署」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1804712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1804712/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1805643/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1805643/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 論黃色經濟圈<br />\n黃圈要長遠發展，好多嘢要一層一層疊上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2000249/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2000249/page/1</a><br />\n黃色經濟圈不等於要求黃絲做義工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1758611/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1758611/page/1</a><br />\n黃色經濟圈最需要嘅唔係創意，而係各行各業的黃店list<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1760146/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1760146/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 論「集體自首」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1436334/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1436334/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 論「公民拘捕權」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1307873/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1307873/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 論「守連儂牆」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1304314/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1304314/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 論「去藍絲群組」洗版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1554564/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1554564/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n論「投票、鬥多like」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1782492/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1782492/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n討論待人處理的態度：<br />\n好多人都分唔到「唔同意你講嘅嘢」同「攻擊你」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1974688/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1974688/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n想大家幫手的Project：<br />\n參加Google map在地嚮導，幫黃店影相、寫評價<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1831096/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1831096/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n維基百科戰線招募長期參與者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1789084/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n反駁藍絲資料庫成立40日，大家估下有幾多人睇過？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1767005/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1767005/page/1</a>"}}